-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_quadrante_medico
-- as
SELECT
[CICLO_QUAD]
,[CRM_QUAD]
,[MERCADO_QUAD]
,[CATEGORIA_QUAD]
,[MKT_SHARE_QUAD]
,[QUADRANTE_QUAD]
,[JORNADA_QUAD]
,[KEY_CRM_UNIV]
,[KEY_CICLO_CRM]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_quadrante_medico_p_*.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) with (
        [CICLO_QUAD]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CRM_QUAD]				VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MERCADO_QUAD]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CATEGORIA_QUAD]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MKT_SHARE_QUAD]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[QUADRANTE_QUAD]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[JORNADA_QUAD]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CRM_UNIV]			VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_CICLO_CRM]		VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) as ROW
